Package: dqmagic
Type: Package
Title: R interface to libmagic
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Ralf Stubner <ralf.stubner@r-institute.com> [aut, cre]"
  ))
Description: The dqmagic package provides an R interface for the libmagic file
  type identification library similar to the Unix file command. This allows for
  file type identification based on a file's content instead of it's extension.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.14)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
URL: https://rinstitute.github.io/dqmagic/
BugReports: https://github.com/RInstitute/dqmagic/issues
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat,
    covr
SystemRequirements: libmagic library and headers
